Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's no time to lose.}{\i0}Không còn thời gian nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It says that a rista dealer\Nwas captured at House Kiltyrin...}Nghe nói tên buôn rista đã bị bắt tại nhà Kiltyrin...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{but are you guys behind that?}hai người đứng sau chuyện này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes. He came after me, um...}Vâng, ông ta bám theo tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{to attack me.}để tấn công.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Was there a huge man with him?}Có tên to lớn nào đi cùng hắn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No.}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If I remember correctly, he was alone.}Hắn đi một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Let's get going, Naut.}{\i0}Đi thôi Naut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The sun's starting to rise.}{\i0}Trời sắp sáng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can see you're taking no chances.}{\i0}Có vẻ không có gì nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I got these\Nat that shop we were just at.}Ờ, lúc nãy ta đã có được ở cửa hàng kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Better than nothing, right?}Thà có còn hơn không.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can stay the way you are.}Ngươi cứ để yên như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Since it's better to make them let\Ntheir guard down, thinking you're just a pig.}Khiến chúng mất cảnh giác\N vì nghĩ ngươi chỉ là một con heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Haste makes waste, you know.}Vội vã sẽ chẳng mang lại tốt lành gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But Blaise is...}{\i0}Nhưng Blaise..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter with Miss Blaise?}Có chuyện gì với Blaise sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, see, we were talking\Nabout how dark the woods are,}{\i0}À không, thì chúng ta sắp đi vào rừng tối,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{so we should get moving\Nwhile the sun's out.}{\i0}nên phải đi nhanh trong khi còn sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, I see.}{\i0}Vậy sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When did you and Blaise\Ndiscuss that?}{\i0}Từ khi nào anh heo nói chuyện với Blaise vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In the middle of the night.}{\i0}Đêm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'd just opened my eyes...}{\i0}Vừa lúc tỉnh lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and Blaise happened to be awake, too.}{\i0}và Blaise cũng thức.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hold onto these.}Giữ thứ này đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll tell you how to use them while we walk.}Tôi sẽ chỉ cô cách dùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A-All right.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come on.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's been bugging you?}{\i0}Nãy giờ anh vội vã gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm checking out the soil and plants\Nto pick out a spot with a lot of moisture.}Kiểm tra đất và thực vật để tìm chỗ nhiều nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Walnut?}{\i0}Óc chó?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There are lots of those near swamps.}{\i0}Có rất nhiều ở khu vực đầm lầy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Unless we're near the water,\Nthose anklets will be useless.}Nếu không gần nơi có nước,\N những cái vòng đó sẽ vô dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ah...}{\i0}A...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hide!}Trốn ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess! Blaise!}{\i0}Jess! Blaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This way!}{\i0}Lối này!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rossi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xử được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{More will be coming.}Chúng sẽ đến nhiều nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A pig!}Một con heo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What do you want?}Ngươi muốn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you one of us?}Các ngươi là trong số chúng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What are you doing with that pig?}Định làm gì với con heo đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's my emergency rations.}Thực phẩm khẩn cấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're hunting with a pig in tow?}Đi săn cùng con heo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's not your pig, is it now?}Đây không phải heo của ngươi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The Yethma we've been searching for\Nshould be around here!}Chắc chắn lũ Yethma chúng ta đang tìm ở gần đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey...}{\i0}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{These guys...}{\i0}Bọn chúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah.}{\i0}Ờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks for before.}Cảm ơn vì khi nãy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Where's the Yethma?}Yethma đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She's nearby, isn't she?}Gần đây phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Dammit!}{\i0}Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've got to do something!}{\i0}Phải làm gì đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm here!}Ở đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Miss Blaise!}{\i0}Blaise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise...}{\i0}Blaise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I knew you were here.}Biết ngay mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What are you doing, Jess?}Cô làm gì thế Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Go back!}Quay lại mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm you, Miss Jess.}{\i0}Tôi là Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Whatever you do, please call me that.}{\i0}Hãy gọi tôi bằng cái tên đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, good girl.}Tốt, gái ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come over here.}Lại đây nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When you get a chance,\Nplease escape with Miss Jess.}{\i0}Khi có sơ hở hãy trốn ngay đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't do that.}{\i0}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ồ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's a fine one you've got there.}Ngon nghẻ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I think the boss might like her.}Có lẽ boss sẽ thích cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Boss?}{\i0}Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Boss, we found her!}Boss, bọn tôi thấy nó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The Yethma traveling with a pig.}Yethma đi cùng con heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Good job!}Làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That guy...}{\i0}Tên đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No way!}Không thể nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've been looking for you...}Tao đang tìm bọn mày...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,tiểu thư Yethma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Here, of all places!}Ở nơi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No question!}{\i0}Không thể nhầm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's the guy who pushed\Nfor Jess's assassination in Kiltyrie!}{\i0}Là tên đã ép tên kia giết Jess ở Kiltyrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, this is the Yethma\Nfrom House Kiltyrin, huh?}Đây là Yethma nhà Kiltyrin à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Quite a fine one, wouldn't you say?}Khá ngon đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- Hey, you bastard!\N- Huh?}Thằng khốn!\N Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't you dare put your filthy hands on her!}Mày thử chạm vào cô ấy xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, boy?}Gì thế nhóc?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is she your woman?}Gái của mày à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Even if it means sacrificing myself,\NI swear you're the one guy I'm gonna kill!}Dù có chết tao cũng kéo mày theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll give you credit\Nfor your grit.}Tao sẽ nhớ đến sự dũng cảm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{you need to learn\Nto read the situation you're in.}mày nên xem xét tình hình đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Five years ago...}Năm năm trước...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Don't you remember the kid\Nwho stole that collar from you guys?}Mày còn nhớ thằng nhóc đã lấy \Nchiếc vòng cổ từ tay mày chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Listen up, Pig.}{\i0}Nghe đây heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We'll start by getting rid\Nof the guy behind me.}{\i0}Đầu tiên là xử tên phía sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}À.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, you're that boy from back then?}Mày là thằng nhãi năm đó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just look how you've grown!}Trưởng thành rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How?}{\i0}Bằng cách nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Those arrows will give us trouble.}{\i0}Những tên cầm cung là phiền nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Use the anklets\Nto divert the enemy's attention.}{\i0}Sử dụng vòng chân làm chúng mất tập trung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then...}{\i0}Sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{we can take on the scrubs\Nin the back for sure.}{\i0}chúng ta sẽ xử lý tên phía sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What about Blaise?}{\i0}Còn Blaise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They wouldn't be too quick to kill a Yethma.}{\i0}Chúng sẽ không giết một Yethma nhanh vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Because there are things they can't do\Nunless she's alive.}{\i0}Vì có những điều chỉ làm được khi còn sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I don't know if I can pull it off.}{\i0}Tuy không biết có suôn sẻ không.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you don't, we're all just going to die.}{\i0}Nhưng nếu không làm thì tất cả sẽ chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I trust you.}{\i0}Ta tin tưởng ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If it works, run to your left!}{\i0}Nếu suôn sẻ hãy chạy về bên trái.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We'll regroup behind that big tree.}{\i0}Chúng ta sẽ hội nhóm tại cái cây lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey...}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why'd you clam up all of a sudden?}Sao tự nhiên lại im lặng thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're scared, maybe?}Ngươi đang sợ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now!}{\i0}Ngay lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You've got a lot of nerve!}Chúng ta đã bất cẩn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It worked, huh?}{\i0}Thành công rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Uh, yeah.}Ờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After you just showed us what you're made of,\Nare you running off again?}Bày trò cho bọn tao xong lại bỏ trốn tiếp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, no matter.}Mà kệ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just sit tight there\Nand watch us toy with this Yethma!}Cứ ở yên đó xem tao chơi đùa với con nhỏ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Pig, when I make a move,\Nyou run to Jess.}{\i0}Heo, khi ta di chuyển thì hãy đến chỗ Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You find a way to escape\Nwhile I'm fighting them!}{\i0}Trong khi ta chiến đấu thì tìm cách thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No...}{\i0}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but...}{\i0}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That Yethma back then...}Yethma khi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now she was what you call quality goods!}Đúng là hàng thượng phẩm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We were so reluctant to kill her...}Bọn tao khó khăn lắm mới quyết định giết nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I think we toyed with her for three days\Nbefore beheading her.}Tao đoán hình như phải 3 ngày làm \Nkhông mệt nghỉ mới cắt đầu nó xuống.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come to think of it, boy...}Nghĩ lại thì nhóc...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{you made off with not only that collar,\Nbut that Yethma's bones, as well.}mày không chỉ lấy vòng cổ mà còn cả xương nữa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Still treasuring them?}Vẫn giữ chúng chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The thing about that Yethma...}Con ả Yethma đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No matter what was done to her,\Nshe was clearheaded until she died.}Dù có làm gì thì nó vẫn tỉnh táo đến lúc chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:13:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{At the very end, she even started\Nsobbing and begging for her life.}Đến phút cuối nó còn khóc lóc cầu xin tha mạng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{what about this Yethma?}con nhỏ này thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She's already been gutted?}Bị rút ruột rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What a fraud, boy!}Gớm nhỉ, thằng nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, that's what this is about.}Chuyện là thế à.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh!}Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Pig, you stick to our priorities!}{\i0}Heo, lo nhiệm vụ của mình đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Get going!}{\i0}Đi đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise, stay crouched down\Nwhere you are!}{\i0}Blaise, ngồi yên đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Crap!}Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Damn!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ice and fire, huh?}Băng và lửa à...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Insolent moves if I ever saw any!}Một thằng nhóc phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Pig. Did you manage to join Jess?}{\i0}Này heo, gặp được Jess chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah! We're good!}{\i0}Rồi! Vẫn ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that right?}{\i0}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then, make a run for it when you can!}{\i0}Thế thì chạy ngay đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Rossi and I will find a way to save Blaise!}{\i0}Rossi và ta sẽ tìm cách cứu Blaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Didn't you swear to kill me\Nif no one else?}Mày thề sẽ giết tao mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise, get on Rossi!}{\i0}Blaise, leo lên Rossi đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Get out of here now!}Đi mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Outta my way!}Đừng có cản trở!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Sorry to disappoint you!}Đáng tiếc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Did it work?}{\i0}Có thành công không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes, that was the perfect spot.}{\i0}Vâng, đúng vị trí luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm going to go save Blaise!}{\i0}Tôi sẽ đi cứu Blaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right. I'm going to go back\Nto where I was...}{\i0}Vâng! Tôi sẽ quay lại vị trí cũ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and wait for you all.}{\i0}và chờ mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the hell was that?}Cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise!}{\i0}Blaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that you, Pig?}{\i0}Ngươi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come on, Blaise! Get on me now!}{\i0}Nào Blaise, lêo lên đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just as I thought,\Nyou're not just some pig.}Quả nhiên ngươi không chỉ là một con heo nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Get on me now!}{\i0}Leo lên mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig! Miss Blaise!}Anh Heo! Blaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess!}{\i0}Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Thank goodness!}{\i0}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad...}Hai người vẫn ổn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{you're both...}là tốt rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{safe!}may quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise...}{\i0}Blaise...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'd lost hope long ago.}{\i0}Tôi đã từng mất đi hi vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I already knew from the start.}{\i0}Vì đã biết từ lâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{On my journey, I was always walking\Nwith my back to the wishing star.}{\i0}Chuyến đi của tôi đã \Nluôn hướng về ngôi sao nguyện ước.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Can you see that red star...}{\i0}Ngôi sao màu đỏ phía bắc...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{in the northern sky?}{\i0}có nhìn thấy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's the wishing star...}{\i0}Đó là ngôi sao nguyện ước.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Salvia.}{\i0}Salvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They say that if you can get your hands\Non that star, your wishes will come true.}{\i0}Họ nói nếu có thể chạm tay vào nó, \Nđiều ước sẽ thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My wishes...}{\i0}Điều ước...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you going now?}{\i0}Chị đi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes.}{\i0}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, I'm never seeing you again.}{\i0}Vậy là... sẽ không gặp lại nhau nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{One last thing before I go.}{\i0}Một chuyện cuối cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When you find yourself at a loss...}{\i0}Khi em cảm thấy lạc lối...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{you should search for a star to guide you.}{\i0}hãy tìm kiếm một vì sao dẫn lối.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Salvia is a wishing star\Nprecisely because it's far off in the northern sky.}{\i0}Salvia vì nằm ở phía xa xôi nhất, \Nnên nó là vì sao ước nguyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When you've lost your way, the wishing star\Nwill show you the direction to take.}{\i0}Khi lạc đường, hãy đi theo hướng của nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And in the same way,\Nwhen you've lost sight of how to live...}{\i0}Và khi lạc lối trong cuộc sống...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{you should search\Nfor a wishing star of your own.}{\i0}hãy tìm kiếm ngôi sao cho bản thân mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Right, I see.}{\i0}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{Live and Go Set Your Feet\Non that Ground}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Miss Blaise!}Blaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's one more Yethma, huh?}Vẫn còn một Yethma nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Dammit, you should've died!}Mẹ nó, mày chịu chết rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mister Pig!}{\i0}Anh Heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that her?}Là nó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After all you did to hide her! Too bad!}Mày đã cố gắng giấu nó, tiếc nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Die!}Chết đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Dammit!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise! Hey! Stay with us!}{\i0}Blaise! Tỉnh lại mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you...}Cảm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{very much.}rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Miss Blaise...}Blaise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Noble Pig...}Anh Heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Promise me...}Hãy hứa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{that Miss Jess will...}rằng Jess sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise!}{\i0}Blaise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise...}{\i0}Blaise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't mess with me, dammit!}Đừng có giỡn mặt tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Pig! Get out of here now!}Heo! Đi mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Death will be my salvation.}{\i0}Cái chết của tôi là sự cứu rỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When I die...}{\i0}Khi tôi chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{please take me to your world, Noble Pig.}{\i0}hãy dẫn tôi đến thế giới của anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That is my...}{\i0}Đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{final wish.}{\i0}nguyện ước cuối cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hurry the hell up!}Nhanh cái chân lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No matter what...}{\i0}Dù có chuyện gì xảy ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I want you all to live...}{\i0}Tôi muốn mọi người phải sống...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and to find happiness.}{\i0}và tìm thấy hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come on, Jess!}{\i0}Đi thôi Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Whatever you do...}{\i0}Nhất định...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{don't die!}{\i0}đừng có chết đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You neither, okay?}{\i0}Cả anh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
